entries.content:
Humans are the most numerous and diverse race, split into various nations and cultures like the Solamnics, Ergothians, and Plainsmen.
The main "barbarian" human cultures in Dragonlance:
Here are all the main human barbarian groups in Dragonlance:
Plainsmen={Horse-riding tribes from Abanasinia, Known for shamans and tribal traditions, Notable tribes: Que-Shu and Que-Kiri}
Ice Folk={Northern warriors adapted to extreme cold, Expert sailors and dogsled handlers}
Khur Nomads={Desert tribes, Skilled traders and horsemen, Strong honor codes}
Mountain Tribes={Independent Kharolis Mountain dwellers, Often clash with dwarves, Expert hunters and climbers}
Sea Barbarians={Raiders and sailors from Northern Ergoth, Fierce naval warriors, Known for longships and coastal raids}
